.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, drawing, cooking, dancing, collecting
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, bus, car, van, subway
There are 5 different favourite beverages: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: card-gamesmaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
5 different games are played: poker, domino, scrabble, bridge, chess
1. the person driving the bike is the person who's hobby is cooking
2. the person driving the swedish is the person playing scrabble
3. the person driving the bus is the person drinking tea
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person drinking coffee
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the person playing domino
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is the dunhill-smoker
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the person driving the van is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing poker
11. the person playing chesss is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the card-gamesmaster-smoker is the person drinking beer
13. the person driving the car is the prince-smoker
14. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking water

.:: Answer ::.
