| Hobby		|    collecting	|     card-games	|      cooking	|     drawing	|     dancing	|
| Transport	|   van	|    bus	|    bike	|    car	|    swedish	|
| Game		|     poker	|    chess	|     domino	|     bridge	|      scrabble	|
| Beverage	|    water	|     tea	|     milk	|    coffee	|      beer	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   card-gamesmaster	|
